[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     13[0m:[38;5;10m[49m This is an exceptionally well-written recipe. The RL formulation is clinically appropriate, the Thompson Sampling approach is the correct choice for this domain, and the regulatory context (FDA 2019 guidance, 21 CFR Part 11) is addressed substantively. The architecture is sound for the stated scale. The "Honest Take" section is genuinely honest about the gap between theoretical elegance and operational reality.
